=== cmd 0: [gen --help] ===
Generate deployment scripts

Usage: treb gen [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  deploy  Generate deployment scripts for contracts and libraries.
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --no-color         Disable colored output (also respected via NO_COLOR env var)
      --non-interactive  Skip interactive prompts (also enabled via TREB_NON_INTERACTIVE=1, CI=true,
                         or non-TTY stdin/stdout)
  -h, --help             Print help
